reviewText: We live Sarah and Duck but this disc would not play in the US

I bought this DVD from my daughter because she love to watch it on Netflix and when I finally tried to play it ...It reads region code error ..... I wish I would have known that DVDs from England or any foreign DVDs aren't compatible with United States DVD players

Did not realize this was region specific and could not play it in our DVD player. I have a truly upset little girl now. :( I understand it was my fault for not fully reading the description but maybe this should be put in the product title as well.
Love love love Sarah and duck. Me and my son can't get enough of it.
They advertised a dvd that do not operate in general/normal USA dvds.  My toddler and i were truly disappointed.
Could NOT play DVD because is from wrong Region....waste of my $
